    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride and it's looking for a new home. It\u2019s been super well-maintained and still runs like a total dream. Whether you need a dependable commuter or something for weekend road trips, this beauty is in great shape and ready to hit the road today. I've absolutely loved driving it, and I know you will too! Come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
